{"type": "article", "id": 17919, "title": "放咖啡制作器具的帆布包", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-23T06:53:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105532WPRMYmI6e9lo8npv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款专放咖啡制作器具的帆布包，为那些喜欢自制咖啡且有移动需要的人提供。帆布包的外形方正，近似一个旅行包，打开后可以看到已划分好的格子，可以放置一套咖啡器皿，包括去毛刺的咖啡研磨机、滴水计时器、来自日本的烧水壶、两个珐琅杯等，售价 349 美元，<a href=\"http://www.timbuk2.com/blue-bottle-sabbatical-travel-kit/581.html?dwvar_581_color=1920&amp;dwvar_581_size=10&amp;utm_source=EEAN-21181&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2-223763&amp;utm_content=1449174793&amp;utm_term=skim77721X1528342Xc181123aedcc0e46906fd9d97aa48c21\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144943N0JPl5KhHXvFbAg4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"637\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144943RPvjrCBmsSNxVa5Z.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144944AavoqyEB92wlgQdY.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144944WdheZmcRNLijSgDT.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}